OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778422284
OL,3,CWatch the moment a dog trapped 6m
OL,4,Cunderground is saved following rescue
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FA team of rescuers have saved a dog
OL,8,Fwhich was trapped more than six metres
OL,9,Funderground on the North York Moors.
OL,11,FScarborough and Ryedale Mountain
OL,12,FRescue Team were called to reports
OL,13,Fthat a dog called Maisy had fallen
OL,14,Fdown a narrow windy pit on Friday, 8
OL,15,FMay.
OL,17,FA spokesperson said the dog had fallen
OL,18,Fthrough several extremely tight gaps,
OL,19,Fwhich likely helped break her fall but
OL,20,Falso left her trapped deep under the
OL,21,Fearth.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
