FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778422284
OL,3,CWatch the moment a dog trapped 6m
OL,4,Cunderground is saved following rescue
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FMountain rescue volunteers were joined
OL,8,Fby fire crews, police and the Upper
OL,9,FWharfdale Fell Rescue Association to
OL,10,Ftry and help Maisy.
OL,12,FThe mission to pull her out took six
OL,13,Fhours in total.
OL,15,FA cave rescuer, Lucy, eventually
OL,16,Fmanaged to squeeze down the tight
OL,17,Fsystem to pull her out.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
