FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778422284
OL,3,CWatch the moment a dog trapped 6m
OL,4,Cunderground is saved following rescue
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FOn a post on social media, the
OL,8,FMountain Rescue team said the mission
OL,9,Frequired "careful assessment and a lot
OL,10,Fof teamwork."
OL,12,FIt added: "Not a bad outcome on Sir
OL,13,FDavid Attenborough's 100th birthday
OL,14,Feither ` proof that people really will
OL,15,Fgo to extraordinary lengths for their
OL,16,Fanimals.
OL,18,F"Huge thanks to everyone involved in
OL,19,Fwhat was a technical, challenging and
OL,20,Fvery muddy rescue!"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
